# Runtime state — never commit these.
# Tracked (shared knowledge): decisions.md, gotchas.md, tech-debt.md
# Everything else is ephemeral per-session/per-branch state.

# Unsupervised flag + threshold + recovery-trigger id
settings.md

# Branch orchestration/blocker notes (## Ship / ## Blocked) and legacy checkpoints
context.md
context-*.md

# Cached rate-limit data (written by statusline.sh where a UI is attached)
usage-cache.json

# Loop log
*.log
